<script>
        // Dark mode script
        const gfgThemeList = Object.freeze({
            LIGHT: "gfgThemeLight",
            DARK: "gfgThemeDark"
        })
        const getThemeFromCookie = () => {
            let gfg_def_theme = "";
            let cookies = document.cookie;
            let cooks = cookies.split(";");
        
            for (let i = 0; i < cooks.length; i++) {
                let icook = cooks[i].split("=");
                if (icook[0].trim() == "gfg_theme") {
                    gfg_def_theme = icook[1].trim();
                }
            }
            return gfg_def_theme
        }
        const toggleNineDotMenuImages = theme => {
            jQuery(".nineDot-menu_left .nineDot-menu_item").each((e, element) => {
                let item = jQuery(element).find("img")
                let imageSrc = item.attr("src")
                let [mainImg, extractImage] = /(.*)\.svg/g.exec(imageSrc)
                if (!mainImg.includes("%40dark") && theme === gfgThemeList.DARK) {
                    mainImg = `${extractImage}%40dark.svg`;
                }
                else if(mainImg.includes("%40dark") && theme === gfgThemeList.LIGHT) {
                    mainImg = `${extractImage.substr(0, extractImage.length - 7)}.svg`;
                }
                item.attr("src", mainImg)
            })
        }

        var isDarkMode = getThemeFromCookie() == gfgThemeList.DARK ? true : false;
        document.querySelector("body").setAttribute("data-dark-mode", isDarkMode);
    </script>

<script>
                                    // Toggle Nine dot menu icons
                                    toggleNineDotMenuImages(isDarkMode ? gfgThemeList.DARK : gfgThemeList.LIGHT)
                                </script>
